      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "That the Inland Empire railway\nis expected to bring in much traf-\nfic to Spokane is seen in the plans\nOF G. w. Weber for the erection Of\nlarge warehouse on Front avenue\nbetween Colfax and Grant streets,\nwithin easy access of the new road.\nMr.. Weber will build at once, and\nas soon as contracts for occupancy\nOF second story are made, will\nincrease the capacity. The site is\n100 by 140 feet."
